title: XIII (French)
description:
The complete series of XIII in French. XIII is a Franco-Belgian comics series very much in the vain of The Bourne Identity, written by Jean Van Hamme and drawn by William Vance. 

The story revolves around a man who washes up on the shore of Peacock Bay on the East Coast of the United States, suffering from amnesia, with only a 'XIII' tattoo to link him to his past. His search to find out who he is and where he came from lead him into confronting the "conspiracy of the XX".

Thanks to the Scanners and enjoy!
